Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:05.62,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:11.59,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:18.26,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:25.23,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:31.02,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:37.91,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.95,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.21,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be20}Promise to find, yes I will
